l-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/26\/prophet-good-akhlaq-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":684,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet teaches good character, manners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was never obscene or immoral. The Prophet would say, \"Verily, among the best of you are those with the best character.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3559, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2321 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":684,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/prophet-never-complain-food\/","url_meta":{"origin":684,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet never criticized food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would never complain about food. If he liked something, he would eat it. If he disliked it, he would leave it. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3370,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2064 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/10\/08\/easy-calm-for-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":684,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sakinah: Make things easy, calm for people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 8, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Make things easy and do not make things difficult. Make people calm and do not frighten them away.\" Source:\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 69,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1734 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/charity-due-every-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":684,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Charity is a duty upon every Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCharity is a duty upon every Muslim.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he has nothing?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen he should work with his hands to benefit himself and give in charity.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/684","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=684"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/684\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=684"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=684"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embe